{"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","title":"setEmails:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:","roleHeading":"Type Method"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user."}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"emails","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Array of email address strings. Each must be a valid email format."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Associates multiple email addresses with the current device for omnichannel","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"email campaigns. This is useful when users have multiple email addresses"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(work, personal, etc.) and want to receive communications on all of them."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All provided emails will be linked to the same device and user ID,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enabling unified targeting across all addresses."}]},{"level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Register multiple emails from user profile:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func syncEmailsFromProfile(_ profile: UserProfile) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primary = profile.primaryEmail {","            emails.append(primary)","        }","        if let secondary = profile.secondaryEmail {","            emails.append(secondary)","        }","        if let work = profile.workEmail {","            emails.append(work)","        }","","        guard !emails.isEmpty else { return }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails)","","        \/\/ Update tags with email count","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"email_count\": emails.count,","            \"has_work_email\": profile.workEmail != nil,","            \"has_multiple_emails\": emails.count > 1","        ])","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:":{"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"title":"setEmails:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:","abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[]}}}